parameters: Hikaru
Tsugumi?
Tsugumi
What is it, at this hour?
Tsugumi
Are you targeting Kanae's recorder too?
Hikaru
No... I just left a book behind and came to pick it up.

I suddenly entered a bright place and couldn't open my
eyes for a while.

Under the fluorescent light in the middle of the night,
Tsugumi's already white skin looked even whiter.
I saw her squinting and wondered what she was doing.
Hikaru
Studying for a test?
Tsugumi
...It's not related to the test, but I was studying.

They might be a little cold, but if you ask them a
question, they will answer properly.

The impression is that she seems to be bad at
relationships with people, but that's probably because
she doesn't like casual interactions and is always
serious.
But it's the test season, so not studying for the test...
I removed the cover of the book she was reading.
A urban legend that destroys the boring daily life...?
Tsugumi

What are you looking at without permission, Mr. Excluding
Window.
Hikaru
U-um, that... why do you have a book about urban legends...?
Tsugumi

......Isn't this the Mystery Club? I don't really understand this
kind of stuff.

Tsugumi, while saying that, averted their eyes slightly as if
embarrassed.

Her face seemed to have turned slightly red, but it's
probably just my imagination.

By the way, Tsugumi joined this club because of Kanae,
right?
As a friend of Kanae, they are very serious.

They must have watched a detective movie somewhere and came
in without thinking about anything.
Tsugumi

What's with that creepy smile? How about you go look for your
forgotten item and leave quickly?
Hikaru

Well, I mean... I was planning on studying for the test
anywhere, but I guess it's fine to study here too.

Tsugumi, who sat next to me in an exaggerated manner, didn't
say anything and handed me a book.
Tsugumi
......Hmph. Do as you please.
It seems like they don't hate it that much.
...Hikaru, ...Hikaru.

I have to study for the test, but suddenly the world
starts shaking.
Hmm, studying...
Studying...?
Hikaru
Ah, ah... what's that...?
